---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ProjectCarousel from '@/components/ProjectCarousel.astro';
import TrustBadges from '@/components/TrustBadges.astro';
const title = "Traffic Generation in Miami — SENAVIA Corp · SEO, SEM & GEO";
const description = "Traffic generation agency in Miami. We combine SEO, paid SEM, and Generative Engine Optimization (GEO) to send qualified visitors to your site across South Florida.";
---
<BaseLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  canonical="/services/traffic-generation"
  jsonLdType="service"
  jsonLdData={{
    name: 'Traffic Generation',
    serviceType: 'Traffic Generation',
    description: 'Integral traffic generation combining SEO, paid SEM, and Generative Engine Optimization (GEO) to drive qualified visitors for South Florida businesses.',
  }}
  screenLabel="Traffic Generation Service"
>
<main>

  <!-- ============================================================
       HERO — Full viewport
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="hero" data-screen-label="01 Traffic Generation Hero">
    <video class="hero-video" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata"
           disablepictureinpicture disableremoteplayback
           controlslist="nodownload nofullscreen noremoteplayback"
           poster="/videos/hero-digital-marketing-poster.jpg">
      <source src="/videos/hero-digital-marketing.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <TrustBadges />
      <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 18px;"><span class="lang-only-en">Traffic Generation · Miami</span><span class="lang-only-es">Generación de Tráfico · Miami</span></div>
      <h1><span class="lang-only-en">A Great Website Means Nothing Without the Right Visitors.</span><span class="lang-only-es">Un Gran Sitio Web No Sirve de Nada Sin los Visitantes Correctos.</span></h1>
      <p class="lang-only-en">An advanced ecosystem that captures customers by combining organic, paid, and AI-driven channels — SEO, SEM, and GEO working as one engine.</p>
      <p class="lang-only-es">Un ecosistema avanzado que captura clientes combinando canales orgánicos, pagados y de inteligencia artificial — SEO, SEM y GEO funcionando como un solo motor.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn" data-calendly-trigger><span class="lang-only-en">Book a Free Call</span><span class="lang-only-es">Agenda tu Llamada Gratis</span></a>
      <div class="metric-strip" aria-label="Key metrics">
        <div class="metric"><span class="metric-value">$12M+</span><span class="metric-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Ad spend managed</span><span class="lang-only-es">Inversión publicitaria gestionada</span></span></div>
        <span class="divider"></span>
        <div class="metric"><span class="metric-value">3.8×</span><span class="metric-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Avg. ROAS lift</span><span class="lang-only-es">Aumento promedio de ROAS</span></span></div>
        <span class="divider"></span>
        <div class="metric"><span class="metric-value">5.0 ★</span><span class="metric-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Google reviews</span><span class="lang-only-es">Reseñas de Google</span></span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       INTRO SPLIT — Premier Traffic Generation Agency + video
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section section--band" data-screen-label="02 Premier Agency">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="split is-reversed" data-reveal>
        <div class="split-copy">
          <div class="eyebrow"><span class="lang-only-en">Why Miami trusts us</span><span class="lang-only-es">Por qué Miami confía en nosotros</span></div>
          <h2><span class="lang-only-en">Premier Traffic Generation Agency in South Florida</span><span class="lang-only-es">Agencia Líder en Generación de Tráfico en el Sur de Florida</span></h2>
          <p class="lang-only-en">A beautiful website is only the first step — without the right visitors, it generates no results. SENAVIA Corp builds an advanced traffic ecosystem for contractors, e-commerce brands, and service businesses across Miami-Dade, Broward, and Palm Beach, capturing customers across every channel that matters today.</p>
          <p class="lang-only-es">Un sitio web atractivo es solo el primer paso — sin los visitantes correctos, no genera resultados. SENAVIA Corp construye un ecosistema avanzado de tráfico para contratistas, marcas de e-commerce y negocios de servicios en Miami-Dade, Broward y Palm Beach, capturando clientes en cada canal que hoy importa.</p>
          <p class="lang-only-en">We combine organic, paid, and AI channels into a single revenue engine: durable SEO authority, high-intent paid campaigns, and content engineered so AI assistants recommend your brand. Our bilingual EN/ES team gives you a partner that speaks your market — and the platforms that serve it.</p>
          <p class="lang-only-es">Combinamos canales orgánicos, pagados y de IA en un solo motor de ingresos: autoridad SEO duradera, campañas pagadas de alta intención y contenido diseñado para que los asistentes de IA recomienden tu marca. Nuestro equipo bilingüe EN/ES te brinda un socio que habla el idioma de tu mercado y de las plataformas que lo atienden.</p>
          <a href="#consultation" class="btn"><span class="lang-only-en">Schedule a Free Consultation</span><span class="lang-only-es">Agenda una Consulta Gratis</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="split-media">
          <div class="video-embed">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Le_xjWf1JMM?rel=0"
              title="SENAVIA Corp — Traffic Generation overview / Generación de Tráfico"
              loading="lazy"
              allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
              allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
          <span class="badge-overlay"><span class="lang-only-en">Google Partner Certified</span><span class="lang-only-es">Certificado Google Partner</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       SUB-PILLARS — SEO · SEM · GEO (Strategy · Purpose · Impact)
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section" data-screen-label="03 Traffic Pillars">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="lang-only-en">The traffic ecosystem</span><span class="lang-only-es">El ecosistema de tráfico</span></div>
        <h2><span class="lang-only-en">Three Engines: SEO, SEM &amp; GEO</span><span class="lang-only-es">Tres Motores: SEO, SEM y GEO</span></h2>
        <p class="lang-only-en">Each channel plays a distinct role across strategy, purpose, and impact — combined, they capture demand from search engines, paid platforms, and AI assistants alike.</p>
        <p class="lang-only-es">Cada canal cumple un rol distinto en estrategia, propósito e impacto — combinados, capturan demanda de los motores de búsqueda, las plataformas pagadas y los asistentes de IA por igual.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3 pillars-grid" data-reveal-children>
        <article class="pillar-card">
          <span class="pillar-tag">SEO</span>
          <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Search Engine Optimization</span><span class="lang-only-es">Optimización para Motores de Búsqueda</span></h3>
          <div class="pillar-rows">
            <div class="pillar-row">
              <span class="pillar-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Strategy</span><span class="lang-only-es">Estrategia</span></span>
              <p class="lang-only-en">Organic channel — long-term semantic optimization.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Canal orgánico — optimización semántica a largo plazo.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-row">
              <span class="pillar-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Purpose</span><span class="lang-only-es">Propósito</span></span>
              <p class="lang-only-en">Build digital authority and durable, long-term semantic optimization across your site.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Construir autoridad digital y una optimización semántica duradera y a largo plazo en todo tu sitio.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-row">
              <span class="pillar-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Impact</span><span class="lang-only-es">Impacto</span></span>
              <p class="lang-only-en">Steady, sustainable qualified organic traffic that lowers customer acquisition cost over time.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Tráfico orgánico calificado, constante y sostenible que reduce el costo de adquisición de clientes con el tiempo.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="pillar-card">
          <span class="pillar-tag">SEM</span>
          <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Search Engine Marketing</span><span class="lang-only-es">Marketing en Motores de Búsqueda</span></h3>
          <div class="pillar-rows">
            <div class="pillar-row">
              <span class="pillar-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Strategy</span><span class="lang-only-es">Estrategia</span></span>
              <p class="lang-only-en">Paid channel — high-intent PPC campaigns.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Canal pagado — campañas PPC de alta intención.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-row">
              <span class="pillar-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Purpose</span><span class="lang-only-es">Propósito</span></span>
              <p class="lang-only-en">Run high-intent paid PPC campaigns on Google Ads and Meta Ads.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Ejecutar campañas PPC pagadas de alta intención en Google Ads y Meta Ads.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-row">
              <span class="pillar-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Impact</span><span class="lang-only-es">Impacto</span></span>
              <p class="lang-only-en">Instant traffic and revenue while organic consolidates, plus fast keyword validation.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Tráfico e ingresos inmediatos mientras lo orgánico se consolida, además de validación rápida de palabras clave.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="pillar-card">
          <span class="pillar-tag">GEO</span>
          <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Generative Engine Optimization</span><span class="lang-only-es">Optimización para Motores Generativos</span></h3>
          <div class="pillar-rows">
            <div class="pillar-row">
              <span class="pillar-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Strategy</span><span class="lang-only-es">Estrategia</span></span>
              <p class="lang-only-en">AI channel — content and data prepared for LLMs.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Canal de IA — contenido y datos preparados para LLMs.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-row">
              <span class="pillar-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Purpose</span><span class="lang-only-es">Propósito</span></span>
              <p class="lang-only-en">Prepare content and structured data so large language models understand your brand.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Preparar el contenido y los datos estructurados para que los modelos de lenguaje entiendan tu marca.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="pillar-row">
              <span class="pillar-label"><span class="lang-only-en">Impact</span><span class="lang-only-es">Impacto</span></span>
              <p class="lang-only-en">Your brand gets recommended as a direct answer in ChatGPT, Gemini, and Perplexity.</p>
              <p class="lang-only-es">Tu marca es recomendada como respuesta directa en ChatGPT, Gemini y Perplexity.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CAPABILITIES — 3 cards
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section section--band" data-screen-label="04 Traffic Capabilities">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="lang-only-en">What we deliver</span><span class="lang-only-es">Qué entregamos</span></div>
        <h2><span class="lang-only-en">Send the Right Visitors To Your Website, Every Day</span><span class="lang-only-es">Lleva los Visitantes Correctos a tu Sitio Web, Todos los Días</span></h2>
        <p class="lang-only-en">Three core capabilities cover the full funnel — high-intent paid search, social demand capture, and durable organic visibility — all feeding one traffic engine.</p>
        <p class="lang-only-es">Tres capacidades clave que cubren todo el embudo: búsqueda pagada de alta intención, captación de demanda en redes sociales y visibilidad orgánica duradera — todas alimentando un solo motor de tráfico.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3" data-reveal-children>
        <article class="cap-card">
          <span class="cap-num">01 · <span class="lang-only-en">Paid Search</span><span class="lang-only-es">Búsqueda Pagada</span></span>
          <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Google Ads &amp; Paid Search</span><span class="lang-only-es">Google Ads y Búsqueda Pagada</span></h3>
          <p class="lang-only-en">Performance campaigns engineered to lower CPA and increase ROAS. Keyword strategy, ad copy, landing-page alignment, and conversion tracking — managed by Google-certified specialists.</p>
          <p class="lang-only-es">Campañas de rendimiento diseñadas para reducir el CPA y aumentar el ROAS. Estrategia de palabras clave, redacción de anuncios, alineación de la página de destino y seguimiento de conversiones, gestionado por especialistas certificados por Google.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="cap-card">
          <span class="cap-num">02 · <span class="lang-only-en">Paid Social</span><span class="lang-only-es">Redes Pagadas</span></span>
          <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Meta Ads &amp; Paid Advertising</span><span class="lang-only-es">Meta Ads y Publicidad Pagada</span></h3>
          <p class="lang-only-en">Facebook &amp; Instagram funnels that drive qualified leads. Audience research, creative production, retargeting flows, and pixel/CAPI setup — built for measurable pipeline.</p>
          <p class="lang-only-es">Embudos de Facebook e Instagram que generan prospectos calificados. Investigación de audiencias, producción creativa, flujos de retargeting y configuración de píxel/CAPI, construidos para un flujo de ventas medible.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="cap-card">
          <span class="cap-num">03 · <span class="lang-only-en">Organic &amp; AI</span><span class="lang-only-es">Orgánico e IA</span></span>
          <h3><span class="lang-only-en">SEO, Local &amp; GEO Positioning</span><span class="lang-only-es">SEO, Local y Posicionamiento GEO</span></h3>
          <p class="lang-only-en">Local SEO, technical SEO, Google Business Profile optimization, and GEO so AI assistants recommend you. Map pack visibility, service-area schema, and content that earns rankings — and answers.</p>
          <p class="lang-only-es">SEO local, SEO técnico, optimización del Perfil de Empresa en Google y GEO para que los asistentes de IA te recomienden. Visibilidad en el paquete de mapas, schema de áreas de servicio y contenido que gana posiciones — y respuestas.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       REASONS — 6-up grid with check icons
       ============================================================ -->
  <section class="section" data-screen-label="05 Why Choose Senavia">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="lang-only-en">Why SENAVIA</span><span class="lang-only-es">Por Qué SENAVIA</span></div>
        <h2><span class="lang-only-en">Why Choose SENAVIA For Traffic Generation In Miami</span><span class="lang-only-es">Por Qué Elegir a SENAVIA Para Generar Tráfico en Miami</span></h2>
        <p class="lang-only-en">Six concrete reasons South Florida businesses pick us over the freelancer down the street and the out-of-state agency upstairs.</p>
        <p class="lang-only-es">Seis razones concretas por las que los negocios del Sur de Florida nos eligen por encima del freelancer de la esquina y de la agencia de otro estado.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="reasons-grid" data-reveal-children>
        <article class="reason-item">
          <span class="check" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="reason-body">
            <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Google Partner-certified team</span><span class="lang-only-es">Equipo certificado como Google Partner</span></h3>
            <p class="lang-only-en">Verified agency status — vetted spend track record and ongoing training on the latest Google products.</p>
            <p class="lang-only-es">Estatus de agencia verificada: historial de inversión comprobado y capacitación continua en los últimos productos de Google.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="reason-item">
          <span class="check" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="reason-body">
            <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Bilingual EN / ES service</span><span class="lang-only-es">Servicio bilingüe EN / ES</span></h3>
            <p class="lang-only-en">Project management, copy, and SEO strategy delivered fluently in both languages — for both audiences.</p>
            <p class="lang-only-es">Gestión de proyectos, redacción y estrategia de SEO con dominio fluido de ambos idiomas, para ambas audiencias.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="reason-item">
          <span class="check" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="reason-body">
            <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Local South Florida expertise</span><span class="lang-only-es">Experiencia local en el Sur de Florida</span></h3>
            <p class="lang-only-en">Deep market knowledge across Miami-Dade, Broward, and Palm Beach — service-area schema, geo-targeted content, the works.</p>
            <p class="lang-only-es">Profundo conocimiento del mercado en Miami-Dade, Broward y Palm Beach: schema de áreas de servicio, contenido geolocalizado y todo lo necesario.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="reason-item">
          <span class="check" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="reason-body">
            <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Transparent reporting &amp; KPIs</span><span class="lang-only-es">Reportes transparentes y KPIs</span></h3>
            <p class="lang-only-en">Live dashboards tied to traffic, leads, and revenue — not just clicks. You always know what each channel is returning.</p>
            <p class="lang-only-es">Paneles en vivo vinculados al tráfico, los prospectos y los ingresos, no solo a clics. Siempre sabes qué retorno genera cada canal.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="reason-item">
          <span class="check" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="reason-body">
            <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Organic + paid + AI in one engine</span><span class="lang-only-es">Orgánico + pagado + IA en un solo motor</span></h3>
            <p class="lang-only-en">SEO, SEM, and GEO orchestrated together — capturing demand at every stage, from cold awareness to bottom-of-funnel intent and AI-driven answers.</p>
            <p class="lang-only-es">SEO, SEM y GEO orquestados en conjunto, captando la demanda en cada etapa, desde el reconocimiento inicial hasta la intención de compra y las respuestas generadas por IA.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="reason-item">
          <span class="check" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
          </span>
          <div class="reason-body">
            <h3><span class="lang-only-en">Ongoing optimization &amp; testing</span><span class="lang-only-es">Optimización y pruebas continuas</span></h3>
            <p class="lang-only-en">Weekly creative refreshes, A/B tests, and bid adjustments — we stay accountable to performance, not just running ads.</p>
            <p class="lang-only-es">Renovaciones creativas semanales, pruebas A/B y ajustes de pujas: somos responsables del rendimiento, no solo de mantener los anuncios activos.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       CONSULTATION — Calendly inline embed
       ============================================================ -->
  <section id="consultation" class="section section--band" data-screen-label="06 Consultation">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="lang-only-en">Free consultation</span><span class="lang-only-es">Consulta gratuita</span></div>
        <h2><span class="lang-only-en">Schedule Your Free Traffic Generation Consultation</span><span class="lang-only-es">Agenda tu Consulta Gratuita de Generación de Tráfico</span></h2>
        <p class="lang-only-en">30 minutes, no commitment. We'll review where your traffic comes from today, identify the biggest wins across SEO, SEM, and GEO, and outline what a SENAVIA-managed engine would look like for your business.</p>
        <p class="lang-only-es">30 minutos, sin compromiso. Revisaremos de dónde proviene tu tráfico hoy, identificaremos las mayores oportunidades en SEO, SEM y GEO, y trazaremos cómo se vería un motor gestionado por SENAVIA para tu negocio.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="calendly-block" data-reveal>
        <div class="calendly-copy">
          <h3><span class="lang-only-en">What you'll walk away with</span><span class="lang-only-es">Con qué te quedarás</span></h3>
          <p class="lang-only-en">A focused conversation tailored to your business goals — actionable next steps you can use whether we work together or not.</p>
          <p class="lang-only-es">Una conversación enfocada y adaptada a los objetivos de tu negocio: pasos prácticos que puedes aplicar, trabajemos juntos o no.</p>
          <ul class="calendly-perks">
            <li><span class="lang-only-en">Quick audit of your current traffic, ad accounts &amp; SEO</span><span class="lang-only-es">Auditoría rápida de tu tráfico, cuentas publicitarias y SEO actuales</span></li>
            <li><span class="lang-only-en">Specific recommendations across SEO, SEM &amp; GEO</span><span class="lang-only-es">Recomendaciones específicas en SEO, SEM y GEO</span></li>
            <li><span class="lang-only-en">Ballpark budget &amp; channel mix if you'd like to move forward</span><span class="lang-only-es">Presupuesto aproximado y combinación de canales si decides avanzar</span></li>
            <li><span class="lang-only-en">No sales pitch — just expert eyes on your funnel</span><span class="lang-only-es">Sin discurso de ventas: solo ojos expertos en tu embudo</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="calendly-inline" id="calendlyInline" role="region" aria-label="Schedule a meeting"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       PORTFOLIO carousel
       ============================================================ -->
  <section id="portfolio" class="section" data-screen-label="07 Portfolio">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
        <h2><span class="lang-only-en">Portfolio &amp; Success Cases</span><span class="lang-only-es">Portafolio y Casos de Éxito</span></h2>
        <p class="lang-only-en">Explore campaigns and digital projects across South Florida — paid media, SEO, and full-funnel strategies built to deliver measurable growth.</p>
        <p class="lang-only-es">Explora campañas y proyectos digitales en todo el Sur de Florida: medios pagados, SEO y estrategias de embudo completo diseñadas para generar un crecimiento medible.</p>
      </div>

      <ProjectCarousel />

      <div class="center-cta">
        <a href="/portfolio" class="btn"><span class="lang-only-en">View All Projects</span><span class="lang-only-es">Ver Todos los Proyectos</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============================================================
       PROCESS + REVIEWS (inside .green-bg)
       ============================================================ -->
  <div class="green-bg">
    <img class="figure f1" src="/images/figure-bg-3.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
    <img class="figure f2" src="/images/figure-bg-2.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">
    <img class="figure f3" src="/images/figure-bg-1.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true">

    <!-- PROCESS -->
    <section id="process" class="section section-flush" data-screen-label="08 Process">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
          <h2><span class="lang-only-en">Our Process</span><span class="lang-only-es">Nuestro Proceso</span></h2>
          <p class="lang-only-en">We understand your goals and challenges, create a tailored plan with clear estimates, and build a custom traffic engine designed for your success.</p>
          <p class="lang-only-es">Entendemos tus objetivos y desafíos, creamos un plan a la medida con estimaciones claras y construimos un motor de tráfico personalizado diseñado para tu éxito.</p>
        </div>
